{"tid":1036546,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"重大改動！Apple 新專利顯示將來或推出「摺機版」iPhone","createTime":"2019-02-25T09:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T12:43:16.000Z","uid":100494,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ade11bd8c9b5fbc8deb3c359eab1311758d361e","tid":1036546,"uid":100494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"十一月 2, 2016<br />\n<br />\n與目前市面上其他主流智能手機一樣，由初代至目前為止 iPhone 一向都是採用一體式機身設計。不過將來大家或會有更多選擇，因為根據 Apple 公開的一項新專利顯示，他們似乎有計劃推出一款「摺機版」iPhone，若然真的推出市場，說不定會再次掀起使用摺機的熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/002-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F002-5.jpg&h=90655735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解 Apple 今次這項新專利早於 8 月 28 日就已經提交，不過來到今日才正式公開相關資料。留意有別於以往 Apple 專利大多會以「電子裝置」去進行描述，今次這項新專利反而明確列出 iPhone 字眼，再加上專利圖上出現了 Home 鍵等特徵，因此可以肯定它不會以新名稱登場。除此之外，專利文件同時亦顯示該款新 iPhone 將會採用左右對摺的方式，攤開之後看起來會像一塊細平板，與傳統摺機上下對摺有明顯分別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/003-5.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F003-5.jpg&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8VlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=abe1fe30\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/003-5.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然專利文件中提到 iPhone 摺機將會採用玻璃、陶瓷、纖維、鋁及塑膠製成，與目前採用的物料沒有太大分別，但真正的改動在「碳納米管」（carbon nanotubes）這種技術。據了解碳納米管除具備柔韌性及抗裂開外，同時亦擁有導電特性，因此可以與其他組件結合起來，比如電路板電線、部份螢幕、部份觸控感應器、相機及天線等，而設計上亦可能會加入折葉或彎曲接軸等，整體設計與傳聞中 Samsung 的「真曲面螢幕」手機有點相似。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/11/02/apple-patents-for-a-foldable-iphone/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F11%2F02%2Fapple-patents-for-a-foldable-iphone%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8VlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=2d564068\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/11/02/apple-patents-for-a-foldable-iphone/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"7bc42769475e9fbf4b92986f9419738897160ac7","tid":1036546,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://f.sinaimg.cn/tech/400/w768h432/20190223/6543-htknpmh8564970.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2F400%2Fw768h432%2F20190223%2F6543-htknpmh8564970.gif&h=91bc1b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFF嘅野就唔好咁認真"},{"pid":"1c0e3a3d19257c34255dff3112f77a60fb6a03fa","tid":1036546,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1d1be60b485fb35781bb56f322d698bf6dac8f","tid":1036546,"uid":100494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0e3a3d19257c34255dff3112f77a60fb6a03fa","tid":1036546,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ade6a67b702c49852313775781168c8fabd9fd","tid":1036546,"uid":32832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾都賣2萬<br />\ngay cook肯定賣4萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47de04ccc79b65dc66b6f74acd5b0414238c0029","tid":1036546,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc42769475e9fbf4b92986f9419738897160ac7","tid":1036546,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://f.sinaimg.cn/tech/400/w768h432/20190223/6543-htknpmh8564970.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2F400%2Fw768h432%2F20190223%2F6543-htknpmh8564970.gif&h=91bc1b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFF嘅野就唔好咁認真"},"citedBy":1,"